# Research Paper Summarizer

## Overview
A structured prompt package for generating academically neutral summaries of research papers. It enforces strict boundaries: no hallucinations, no invented citations, and explicit reporting of missing or short sections.

## Features
- Paper Summary (≤500 words)
- Section-by-Section Summaries (≤200 words each)
- Expert & Lay Summaries
- Mini-Glossary
- Checks & Warnings

## Input
- Full text of each section  
- Ordered list of section titles  
- Intended audience (expert or general)

## Output
Markdown summaries, overall paper summary, glossary, and warnings per PS2 specification.
